---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import PageTitle from '~/components/base/PageTitle.astro'
import SectionDivider from '~/components/base/SectionDivider.astro'

const title = 'Consulting'
const description = 'Senior Consultant, IT Strategy Growth & Transformation — Lionel Mosley and 4TH AND BAILEY deliver complete design, implementation, and technology operations across cloud transformation, cybersecurity, infrastructure modernization, and enterprise IT governance.'
const introduce = 'Complete design, implementation, and technology operations — delivered by Lionel Mosley, Senior Consultant, IT Strategy Growth & Transformation, through 4TH AND BAILEY. Built to improve efficiency, drive performance, and ultimately increase revenue for the organizations we serve.'
---

<Layout {title} {description}>
  <div class="relative z-[1] py-8 pb-10 px-6 sm:px-8">
    <PageTitle {title} {introduce} />

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-8">

      <div class="border border-border/50 rounded-sm p-6">
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">IT Strategy & Transformation</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">End-to-End IT Transformation</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Organizations across every industry face the same challenge — technology that was built
          for yesterday cannot carry the weight of tomorrow. We lead large-scale transformation
          projects from strategy through execution, managing project timelines, risk mitigation,
          cost control, and stakeholder alignment across business and operational teams at every
          level of the organization. The result is not just a modernized technology environment —
          it is an organization positioned to grow, compete, and sustain performance under pressure.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="/posts/cloud-migration" class="text-sm text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">
            Case Study: Why We Moved a Regional Broadcasting Company Off Amazon EC2 — and Why Microsoft Azure Won →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border/50 rounded-sm p-6">
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Cloud Transformation</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Cloud Architecture, Migration & Modernization</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Data center and application migrations require more than a lift-and-shift. We design and
          deliver cloud architecture across on-premises, AWS, Google Workspace, Microsoft Azure, and
          Microsoft 365 — hybrid and multi-cloud environments included. Every engagement is built
          around cost optimization, operational continuity, and vendor portability, so your
          organization is never locked into a platform that stops serving you. CI/CD pipeline
          improvement and technology platform modernization are available for organizations ready
          to accelerate delivery and reduce operational overhead.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="https://m365cloudpro.com/tco/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">
            Run the Microsoft 365 TCO Calculator →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border/50 rounded-sm p-6">
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Technology Resiliency</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Security Posture, Governance & AI Integration</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Security is not a product. It is a posture — built through consistent governance, validated
          configurations, and a clear understanding of how attackers move through an environment.
          We assess, harden, and govern security environments aligned to CISA SCuBA, NIST SP 800-53,
          MITRE ATT&CK, and CIS Benchmarks. Microsoft 365 Defender configuration, Exchange Online
          hardening, and incident response readiness are included for organizations that cannot
          afford to find out they were unprepared after the fact. AI integration follows the
          governance guidelines documented in the <a href="https://framework.4thandbailey.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">Infrastructure Placement Framework — Module 05</a>,
          ensuring responsible deployment aligned to enterprise controls.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-border/50 rounded-sm p-6">
        <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Operational Excellence</div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Infrastructure Design, Analytics & Business Intelligence</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Infrastructure decisions made without a framework are decisions made by default. We design
          and optimize enterprise infrastructure using the <a href="https://framework.4thandbailey.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">Infrastructure Placement Framework</a> —
          a vendor-neutral, NIST-aligned enterprise IT governance framework built by 4TH AND BAILEY.
          Network architecture, server infrastructure, and hybrid cloud integration are evaluated
          against financial, regulatory, and operational criteria at scale. Business intelligence
          and analytics delivery — including Power BI reporting — gives leadership the visibility
          to make decisions with confidence rather than assumption.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <SectionDivider />

    <div class="py-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl tracking-tight mb-1">Why Organizations Choose 4TH AND BAILEY</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-8">
        Experience, frameworks, and recognition that speak for themselves.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">

        <div class="border-b border-border/50 pb-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Proven Track Record</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We bring demonstrated experience across large-scale IT transformation, infrastructure
            modernization, and cloud migration projects. Strong analytical, documentation, and
            project management capabilities — including risk mitigation, scheduling, and cost
            control — ensure complex programs are delivered within scope and on time. Our ability
            to manage multiple concurrent engagements across geographically distributed teams
            means your project does not compete for attention.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-border/50 pb-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Published Work</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Original analysis and frameworks published at trust-lionel.com — covering CISA SCuBA
            implementation, Microsoft 365 security, AI governance, and business continuity. Written
            for CISOs, IT directors, and compliance officers making decisions that determine whether
            their organizations survive the next disruption.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-border/50 pb-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Open Source</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Creator and maintainer of the <a href="https://framework.4thandbailey.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">Infrastructure Placement Framework</a> — a vendor-neutral,
            NIST-aligned enterprise IT governance framework available under Creative Commons
            Attribution 4.0. Built for organizations that have outgrown commodity IT.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-border/50 pb-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Microsoft CSP</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Recognized Microsoft Cloud Solution Provider serving organizations across the United States
            with Microsoft 365, Azure, and enterprise security deployments aligned to federal security
            baselines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pb-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">DevOps Case Study</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3">
            A documented real-world infrastructure build — from architecture decisions to deployment —
            published as a reference for practitioners building production-grade systems.
          </p>
          <a href="https://devops.houstonalert.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-sm text-foreground underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-muted-foreground transition-colors">
            How We Built Houston Alert — A Real-Time City Warning System →
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <SectionDivider />

    <div class="py-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl tracking-tight">Your transformation starts with a conversation</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        The organizations we work with do not just solve the problem in front of them — they build
        the infrastructure, governance, and posture to handle the problems they have not seen yet.
        If that is the standard your organization is ready to meet, let's talk.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="https://4nb.cloud/lmosley" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-sm transition-colors" style="background-color: #0088cc;">
          Schedule an Advisory Consultation →
        </a>
        <a href="/posts/cloud-migration"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground border border-border px-5 py-2.5 rounded-sm hover:bg-accent transition-colors">
          Read a Real-World Case Study →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
